            // |  TAB  |  A  |  S  |  D   |  F   |  G   |                         |  H   |  J    |  K    |  L   |   ;   |   '   |
            // | SHIFT |  Z  |  X  |  C   |  V   |  B   |  MUTE  |        | ExtPw |  N   |  M    |  ,    |  .   |   /   | SHIFT |
            //               | LEFT|RIGHT | LOWER| BSCP |  ENTER |        | ENTER | SPACE|  DEL  |  UP   | DOWN |

            bindings = <
&kp ESC    &kp N1  &kp N2    &kp N3     &kp N4  &kp N5                                       &kp N6     &kp N7   &kp N8     &kp N9    &kp N0    &kp GRAVE
&kp TAB    &kp Q   &kp W     &kp E      &kp R   &kp T                                        &kp Y      &kp U    &kp I      &kp O     &kp P     &kp SQT
&kp LSHFT  &kp A   &kp S     &kp D      &kp F   &kp G                                        &kp H      &kp J    &kp K      &kp L     &kp SEMI  &kp LBKT
&kp LCTRL  &kp Z   &kp X     &kp C      &kp V   &kp B     &kp C_MUTE      &ext_power EP_TOG  &kp N      &kp M    &kp COMMA  &kp DOT   &kp FSLH  &kp RBKT
                   &kp LEFT  &kp RIGHT  &mo 1   &kp BSPC  &kp LEFT_ALT    &kp ENTER          &kp SPACE  &kp DEL  &kp UP     &kp DOWN
            >;

            sensor-bindings =
                <&inc_dec_kp C_VOL_DN C_VOL_UP>,
